titles.title: A resolution notifying the House of Representatives of the election of a Sergeant at Arms and Doorkeeper of the Senate.

vote.text: Submitted in the Senate, considered, and agreed to without amendment by Unanimous Consent.

action.text: Message on Senate action sent to the House.

bill.summary: 1/4/2007--Passed Senate without amendment. (This measure has not been amended since it was introduced. The summary of that version is repeated here.) Requires notification of the House of Representatives of the election of Terrance W. Gainer as Sergeant at Arms and Doorkeeper of the Senate.
